node.text:
In September, we asked you to show us the world through your lenses—to capture life's most meaningful moments. The result was 29,000 #GoProHERO9 Black submissions from 125 countries. Today, 56 of those submissions compose 2 minutes of what it means to be part of the #GoProFamily. From backyards, to backcountry, + beyond, this was created by you, for you. Congratulations to the 56 #GoProAward recipients taking home $17,857 each. 🤑
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Tap the link in our bio for the full list of recipients #GoPro #HyperSmooth #TimeWarp #GoProSnow #GoProSurf #GoProMTB
